---
title: Coconut Fish & Makrut Lime Sauce with Jasmine Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: We’re going nuts for this aromatic coconut sauce infused with the citrus of makrut lime leaves. Top your golden fish fillets and stir-fried Asian veggies with this saucy delight and let the jasmine rice soak up the rest for a truly spectacular taste sensation.
